module-help "
GROMACS (GROningen MAchine for Chemical Simulations) is a free, open-source
software suite designed for high-performance molecular dynamics (MD)
simulations. It models the physical movements of atoms and molecules, allowing
scientists to analyze biological processes like protein folding, lipid membrane
dynamics, and drug interactions.
"
